<Layout
  title="Summer Lash Extension Care Tips | Orange County Beach Guide"
  description="Hot weather and summer activities require special lash extension care. Expert summer tips from Orange County lash professionals."
  keywords="summer lash care, beach lashes, pool lashes, Orange County summer, lash extension swimming"
